Q: 24/7 Jet Inc.在2024年每个月的飞行量是多少？按从大到小排列。
SQL:
SELECT
    p.date_month,
    COUNT(*) AS num
FROM
    zts_plane_flight_1 AS p
INNER JOIN
    aircraft_details AS a
ON
    p.pure_reg = a.pure_reg
WHERE
    a.supplier_id = "1001" AND p.date_month BETWEEN '2024-01' AND '2024-12'
GROUP BY
    p.date_month
ORDER BY
    num DESC;

SELECT
    p.date_month,
    COUNT(*) AS num
FROM
    zts_plane_flight_1 AS p
INNER JOIN
    aircraft_details AS a
ON
    p.pure_reg = a.pure_reg
WHERE
    a.supplier_id = "1067" AND p.date_month BETWEEN '2024-01' AND '2024-12'
GROUP BY
    p.date_month
ORDER BY
    num DESC;
